sentences: Joel Prince (born November 3, 1986), also known as J Prince, is a gospel Soca artiste and EDM producer from Trinidad and Tobago.
In 2008 he changed his name to J Prince and released his first single, "Victory" produced by G Master.
In 2011 J Prince and Flow Master Records released his first two albums, 'Omega - A New Beginning', and 'Renaissance'.
Producer Roger Ryan signed J Prince to After Touch Music in 2016.
